Baseless rumors? I'm not making this up.

168
00:13:05,326 --> 00:13:06,285
Now…

169
00:13:06,994 --> 00:13:09,705
This is Asung Academy, not Asung High.

170
00:13:10,498 --> 00:13:12,583
