because she worked closely with me.

183
00:13:56,293 --> 00:13:59,421
That's Minister Kyung Woo-min,
Senator Sung Min-joon.

184
00:13:59,505 --> 00:14:01,423
Hankook University Professor,
Son Seung-yeon,

185
00:14:01,507 --> 00:14:03,592
