the same accessory on her handbag.

208
00:15:28,218 --> 00:15:30,262
It must be a similar item.

209
00:15:31,263 --> 00:15:34,558
I didn't sleep well last night,
so I don't look so great.

210
00:15:44,401 --> 00:15:45,527
