221
00:16:17,226 --> 00:16:21,063
about you and Ms. Ji to cover up
Ye-lin's cheating scandal?

222
00:16:22,106 --> 00:16:24,233
-Yes.
-Forget it.

223
00:16:24,942 --> 00:16:26,819
