but the judge dismissed them.

224
00:16:26,902 --> 00:16:28,404
Bringing it up now won't change anything.

225
00:16:28,487 --> 00:16:29,863
So I have to handle it
before it's too late.

226
00:16:29,947 --> 00:16:31,532
